snippet.title: Go-Go Town! Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Plan, Build...Prosper?  As mayor, it’s up to you to breathe life back into this rundown town. Construct shops, hire staff, automate deliveries with couriers, and attract tourists to town, all while managing infrastructure and avoiding catastrophes! 

Welcome to Go-Go Town! You’re going to do great.

Wishlist now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2195120/GoGo_Town/
